StringValues.16: A buadren fashioned by Aun Aulakhe to invoke the spirit of Aun Tanua from his Virindi prison in portal space.
StringValues.15: A buadren fashioned by Aun Aulakhe.
StringValues.7: Even in captivity, Tanua still fights against the enemies of his people.
StringValues.14: This item can be used on floor and wall hooks.
